room_title: Escape room "The Incident" by Key To Escape in Nashua
room_description:
The adventure begins on December 31st, 1999, 10:30 pm. Everyone is preparing to update their computer software in wake of the Y2K scare. Well, everyone except you. You received a message asking for help from Jasmine, an old friend. When you arrive in her apartment, you realize Jasmine’s years of conspiracy theorizing has paid off.
She’s become privy to an alien attack on our technology. Luckily for you, and all of the human race, Jasmine has found a way to prevent the attack, however, her and her software have vanished! Can you find and implement her software before midnight?
